- New inventories for 2013-2014 developed according to 2006 IPCC guidelines;
- Inventory for 2012 recalculated to fine-tune the data by use of official data from the State Statistical Office published after the submission of the FBUR;
- Quality of the whole series of the GHG Inventory 1990-2014 improved by introduction of higher Tier to the extent possible;
- Second Biennial Update Report preparation started, team members contracted, participatory approach ensured.

